00:31:02,360 --> 00:31:05,040
 not be in vain.

556
00:31:05,040 --> 00:31:08,520
 So let me give us a couple of things that we can do, a couple of little practical steps

557
00:31:08,520 --> 00:31:14,240
 that we can take in order to address the fear in our hearts, in order to address the anxiety

558
00:31:14,240 --> 00:31:20,360
 that we feel, in order to find some sense of peace and stability here and now.

559
00:31:20,360 --> 00:31:24,560
 The first thing is this, it's a realization that we have to keep with us.

560
00:31:24,560 --> 00:31:32,240
 We must first realize that we are positioned for success when we are dependent on God.

561
00:31:32,240 --> 00:31:37,640
 Not when we're dependent on ourselves, not when we're dependent on our paychecks or on

562
00:31:37,640 --> 00:31:42,800
 our GPAs or on the people that we know, but when we are dependent on God.

563
00:31:42,800 --> 00:31:47,680
 God builds and guards by his grace, therefore we need him.

564
00:31:47,680 --> 00:31:49,520
 We need him.

565
00:31:49,520 --> 00:31:55,320
 John would say in the New Testament that apart from him, we can do nothing, right?

566
00:31:55,320 --> 00:31:57,400
 He's the vine where the branch is, apart from him, we can do nothing.

567
00:31:57,400 --> 00:32:03,180
 But then Paul would say that I can do all things through him.

568
00:32:03,180 --> 00:32:09,240
 You see that this big thing that we have to have God as a part of it.

569
00:32:09,240 --> 00:32:13,080
 We're dependent on him and one of the best ways that we can be dependent practically,

570
00:32:13,080 --> 00:32:18,040
 I was going to get practical, is this thing called a Sabbath.

571
00:32:18,040 --> 00:32:19,520
 Now I know it's not popular.

572
00:32:19,520 --> 00:32:21,240
 It probably sounds like some old Hebrew word.

573
00:32:21,240 --> 00:32:24,960
 I think it is an old Hebrew word.

574
00:32:24,960 --> 00:32:28,960
 But the Sabbath was instituted from the very beginning for us, for our good.

575
00:32:28,960 --> 00:32:36,800
 We look back at the creation story and we see that after six days of working, God rests.

576
00:32:36,800 --> 00:32:41,480
 And perhaps that is a pattern that we are meant to live within.

577
00:32:41,480 --> 00:32:47,360
 Perhaps God is actually asking us to take a day where we don't assume the position of

