00:34:35,000 --> 00:34:37,520
 Maybe we can get honest with God.

610
00:34:37,520 --> 00:34:41,560
 He doesn't just want to hear your good thoughts and your good prayers.

611
00:34:41,560 --> 00:34:42,560
 Get real with him.

612
00:34:42,560 --> 00:34:45,640
 Tell him that you hurt.

613
00:34:45,640 --> 00:34:48,160
 Tell him where it hurts and tell him why.

614
00:34:48,160 --> 00:34:50,040
 Tell him the things that are on your heart.

615
00:34:50,040 --> 00:34:52,080
 Bring to him your actual fears.

